Pyro.name: Pyro
Pyro.description: Pyro is the fire element. It's the strongest purely fire-based element.

Hydro.name: Hydro
Hydro.description: Hydro is the water element. It's the strongest purely water-based element.

Anemo.name: Anemo
Anemo.description: Anemo is the air element. It's the strongest purely air-based element.

Electro.name: Electro
Electro.description: Electro is the electric element. It's the strongest purely electric-based element.

Geo.name: Geo
Geo.description: Geo is the earth element. It's the strongest purely earth-based element.

Normal.name: Normal
Normal.description: Normal is the neutral element. It's not particularly strong against anything.
